data.description: Fantastic and beautiful two-story home READY FOR MOVE-IN! This home features an open floor concept and the added kitchen cabinets give you ample storage room.  The primary bedroom suite has a washer/dryer in the closet to make it convenient while the spacious laundry room upstairs is for the other 3 bedrooms. A spacious family room/game room upstairs that can be used for whatever you desire. The backyard is fenced with NO BACK NEIGHBORS. Neighborhood amenities include multiple playgrounds, plenty of walking trails and a beautiful community pool. Minutes away from shopping and dining the The Woodlands and zoned to the Conroe ISD. Schedule your showing now! Seller is willing to give $5000 to help buyers buy down interest rate.
